msgid "Scenario IV: Return to The Wages of Sin"
msgstr "冒险IV：重返恶罪报应"

msgid "Set the Erynn MacAoidh story asset aside, out of play."
msgstr "将伊琳·麦凯剧情支援放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid "When building the act deck, use the new Act 1a—\"In Pursuit of Answers\" instead of the original act 1, and include both versions of act 2. When advancing to act 2a, put both act cards into play; the text on both cards is active."
msgstr "在构建场景牌堆时，不使用原版的场景1，改为使用新版场景1a - “追寻答案”，并加入两个版本的场景2。在推进到场景2a时，将两张场景卡都放置入场；两张卡上的文本同时生效。"

msgid "Remove the new act cards included in the <i>Return to the Wages of Sin</i> encounter set from the game."
msgstr "将<i>重返恶罪报应</i>遭遇组中的新版场景卡移出游戏。"

msgid "Randomly choose one of the two The Gallows locations, one of the two Heretics’ Graves locations, one of the two Chapel Attic locations, one of the two Chapel Crypt locations, and one of the two Hangman's Brook locations, and put them into play. Remove the other versions of The Gallows, Heretics’ Graves, Chapel Attic, Chapel Crypt, and Hangman's Brook from the game. Then, put Haunted Fields and Abandoned Chapel into play."
msgstr "随机从以下每种地点中各选1个：绞刑架、异端者的墓地、教堂阁楼、教堂地下室、绞刑者河，然后将选出的5个地点放置入场。将所选地点的其他版本移出游戏。然后，将闹鬼农田、废弃教堂放置入场。"

msgid "Shuffle the eight Heretic enemies and set aside four of them, at random. Remove the other four copies from the game. These cards are double-sided and have story cards on their reverse side. For the best experience, do not look at the story cards on their other side."
msgstr "混洗8张异端者敌人，将其中随机4张放在一边。将其他4张移出游戏。这些卡牌是双面的，其背面为剧情卡。为了获得最佳的游戏体验，请勿查看背面内容。"

msgid "In your Campaign Log, record <i>1 heretic was unleashed unto Arkham.</i>"
msgstr "在冒险日志记录下<i>有1名异端者被释放到阿卡姆。</i>"

msgid "In your Campaign Log, record that <i>Erynn joined the investigators</i>. Any one investigator may choose to add Erynn MacAoidh to their deck. This card does not count toward that investigator’s deck size."
msgstr "在冒险日志记录下<i>伊琳加入了调查员</i>。任意一位调查员可以选择将伊琳·麦凯剧情支援加入其牌组。这张卡牌不计入该调查员的牌组张数上限。"

msgid "Erynn joined the investigators."
msgstr "伊琳加入了调查员。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rule applies:\n"
"\"While resolving The Watcher's Grasp treachery, The Spectral Watcher does not exhaust after it attacks.\"\n"
"Attach the Return to The Wages of Sin card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"在本场冒险接下来的时间里，增加以下额外规则：\n"
"“结算看守人的攫噬诡计时，幽灵看守人在攻击后不消耗。”\n"
"将重返恶罪报应卡牌叠加到冒险辅助卡上，以作提示。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Hanged Man · XII\" in the reversed position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是逆位的“倒吊人·XII”。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Hanged Man · XII\" in the upright position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是正位的“倒吊人·XII”。"

msgid "As you depart Hangman's Hill, the unnatural mist lingers behind—a reminder that you chose information and power over the safety of the city. The last thing you see as you cross the brook is the blood streaking down the bark of the trees flanking the bridge. The sight is repulsive, and yet… perhaps there is information to be gathered here, as well. Hoping you've done the right thing, you study the strange carving for a moment before continuing to your next destination."
msgstr "你离开绞刑者山丘时，那团怪雾仍在身后不见消散——这提醒著你，相比于城市的安全，你选择了情报和力量。穿过小溪时，你注意到桥边的树皮上，有血液正向下流淌。这一幕令人作呕，但……也许这里也有值得收集的情报。你研究了一会那怪异的雕刻，心中希望自己所做的是正确的，然后站起身，向下一个目的地出发。"
